tags: Doctor friendliness,Explanation of the health issue,Treatment satisfaction,Value for money,
review: Doctor Manak is a qualified professional. Hygiene of the clinic is of very high standards. Precise actions by the doctor help less tension and repetition. I am having his dental services for almost a decade.

Surgery and that too dental surgery it just made me scared. Heard lot of experience of people who had dental surgery and had pain. Top of that I just googled and saw the complete procedure of extraction and implant on you tube. It was damn scary ... I neglected my dental implant and surgery for a long time. Even after getting appointment I took 2 mnths time. Atlast I went to Dr Manak. On the day of surgery we had opted for immediate implant...I was so scared...but he convinced me by saying "if you even have a small pain raise your hand and we won't do the procedure". Yes, he was right. Procedure took time as I had both side tooth extraction too but I never felt a pain. No pain during the implant procedure also. Awesome..only proper medication I took I never had pain. My whole family was so sceptic...oooh God...but I told it was not painful. They are still wondering...and they thought after anasthesia wears off there will be complaints but no even after the procedure I never felt if any implant was done.  Thank you thank you Dr Manak.....u just changed my whole perspective regarding dental surgeries....and thank you for doing a painless and smooth procedure. Thanks a lot.....u r awesome....
reply_text: thats one of the best reviews received by us mam, thanks a ton for such kind and encouraging words. we wish to keep serving you and all other patients in the best of our spirits and hope everytime any dental issue troubles you, we r there to help you get rid of it. as a patient you have been very cooperative and have followed all the post operative instructions nicely. thanks for trusting us with the implant work.

tags: Doctor friendliness,Explanation of the health issue,Treatment satisfaction,
review:
I have visited Dr. Manak for RCT and I’m really happy and satisfied with his treatment. He literally has magic in his hands and he is so kind and friendly.

I had RCT from 3 different doctors and I had very bad experience previously and I was very traumatized before and really didn’t wanted to visit any dentist.

I read about Dr. Manak and after looking at his reviews I decided to visit his clinic. After my first siting I can say that I have made the best decision of my life, it’s was completely painless. Even when he pricked me for local anesthesia, I didn’t feel any pain.

I would definitely recommend him, you can visit him for any dental related problem ** ***** ** ** **** *** ****** *** **** ******* *** experienced in his field.

Thank You Dr. Manak. God Bless You. You are really a wonderful doctor.

I had booked an appointment and reached 10 minutes prior to the scheduled time. I could see another patient known to the doctor, who came after me being treated ahead of me. I had to wait for more than 1hr after which doctor checked me and explained me  that I will require 2-3 dental fillings and scaling. But I was really surprised to know that I will have to come back after 7 days. Doctor mentioned that he is completely occupied for the week and made me pay consultation charges to make sure I come back next week. But his practo schedule showed majority of the slots unbooked. **** ** ****** ************** *** **** * ******** ** **** **** ********* I would request practo to monitor this properly so that patients don't spend their precious time waiting. I booked an appointment with another doctor and got the procedure done next morning in a single seating ******* ** ******* *** * ******** **** * I am very satisfied with my decision.

tags: Doctor friendliness,Explanation of the health issue,Treatment satisfaction,
review:
*** ***** ** ** ********* ******* *** ** very soft spoken and a professional dentist .About 7-8 years ago i got my tooth filling done by him. And till now those fillings are intact n strong. Last year i got tooth fillings done in some other tooth and in some other dental clinic but within 5-6 months it came off..I was very disappointed.. So i tried to look again for Dr Manak and by God's grace i am happy to found his clinic. Now after 7-8 years i got my tooth filling done by Dr Manak and i am very happy with his work, his practical hand is very light my treatment was completely painless. I would refer him for others also. Moreover he is such a patient doctor that he listens attentively and clears our doubts and queries in detail.He takes time to explain every procedure he is going to do along with it's risk involved. I would recommend Dr. Manak to everyone. Thankyou very much Doctor & staff.
Regards 
Aafreen
